 Migration Strategy: The "Heavy Lift" Rule

Only migrate logic to Wasm if:

Computation is heavy (math, rendering, encryption)

Interaction with JavaScript is minimal (avoid chatty interfaces)

You have existing .NET/C++ code (porting vs. rewriting)



